{"data":[{"date":"11:08 27/06","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Maradona nh\u1eadp vi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea9n c\u1ea5p sau tr\u1eadn Nigeria 1-2 Argentina","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/huyen-thoai-maradona-nhap-vien-khan-cap-sau-tran-nigeria-12-argentina.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"3848","checkdouble":"189721"},{"date":"11:19 27/06","title":"N\u01b0\u0303 C\u0110V quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 nh\u00e2\u0301t World Cup 2018 phu\u0309 nh\u00e2\u0323n \u0111o\u0301ng phim c\u1ea5p 3","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/27/nu-cdv-quyen-ru-nhat-world-cup-2018-phu-nhan-dong-phim-cap-3.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Natalya Nemchinova cho hay nh\u01b0\u0303ng hi\u0300nh a\u0309nh kho\u0309a th\u00e2n cu\u0309a c\u00f4 lan truy\u00ea\u0300n tr\u00ean ma\u0323ng la\u0300 do ba\u0323n trai cu\u0303 pha\u0301t ta\u0301n. </h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><br />\r\nNemchinova, 28 tu\u1ed5i, h\u00f4m 26/6 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau khi xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n kh\u1eafp c\u00e1c m\u1eb7t b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 World Cup trong hai tu\u1ea7n qua. C\u00f4 cho hay m\u00ecnh kh\u00f3c su\u1ed1t \u0111\u00eam v\u00ec b\u1ecb m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 sao phim xxx. \"Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t c\u0169\", Sun d\u1eabn l\u1eddi c\u00f4 k\u1ec3. \"C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 5 n\u0103m, t\u00f4i v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e0ng trai tr\u1ebb y\u00eau nhau. Khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i chia tay, anh ta quay l\u1ea1i ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u t\u00f4i. Anh ta \u0111\u0103ng m\u1ed9t video t\u1ef1 quay \u1edf nh\u00e0 l\u00ean m\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 khi m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u\".<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNemchinova kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f4 ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd l\u00e0m di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean phim c\u1ea5p 3: \"T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd b\u00e1n c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 m\u00ecnh v\u00ec ti\u1ec1n. T\u00f4i thi tho\u1ea3ng l\u00e0m ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eabu nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1edf th\u00edch c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean\".<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"N\u01b0\u0303 C\u0110V quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 nh\u00e2\u0301t World Cup 2018 phu\u0309 nh\u00e2\u0323n \u0111o\u0301ng phim c\u1ea5p 3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"N\u01b0\u0303 C\u0110V quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 nh\u00e2\u0301t World Cup 2018 phu\u0309 nh\u00e2\u0323n \u0111o\u0301ng phim c\u1ea5p 3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/NINTCHDBPICT000416028828-7797-9783-9061-1530063383.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Natalya Nemchinova tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i c\u1ed5 v\u0169 cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Nga \u1edf s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng Samara h\u00f4m 25/6. \u1ea2nh: AFP</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb9p t\u00f3c v\u00e0ng 28 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i l\u00e0 n\u1eef C\u0110V quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 sau khi xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga v\u1edbi trang ph\u1ee5c g\u1ee3i c\u1ea3m. C\u00f4 th\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1eb7c \u00e1o d\u00e2y tr\u1eafng, qu\u1ea7n b\u00f3 s\u00e1t v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfc m\u0169 truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nTh\u00f4ng qua FAN ID, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng m\u1ea1ng \u1edf Nga \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm ra danh t\u00ednh c\u00f9ng nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh, video n\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a c\u00f4 v\u00e0 cho c\u00f4 l\u00e0 sao c\u1ea5p 3.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNemchinova n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng c\u00f4 ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebfng g\u00ec v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i. C\u00f4 ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng ch\u00fang ch\u00fa \u00fd sau khi b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o. \"T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f3c, t\u00f4i may m\u1eafn khi c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 h\u1ecd bi\u1ebft t\u00f4i l\u00e0 ai\", c\u00f4 n\u00f3i. Nemchinova mu\u1ed1n d\u1eb9p b\u1ecf nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n kh\u00f4ng hay v\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng tai ti\u1ebfng s\u1ebd s\u1edbm k\u1ebft th\u00fac.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nB\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng chuy\u1ec7n x\u1ea3y ra, Nemchinova cho hay c\u00f4 v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Nga t\u1ea1i World Cup. \"T\u00f4i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t sau Euro 2012. T\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn Ba Lan v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u00f4i \u0111i c\u1ed5 v\u0169 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ebfn Brazil v\u00e0o World Cup 2014 v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o Euro 2016\", c\u00f4 n\u00f3i.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3847","checkdouble":"189723"},{"date":"10:16 27/06","title":"C\u1ef1c b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Fellaini","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/cuc-bat-ngo-voi-ben-do-tiep-theo-cua-fellaini.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo m\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n tin c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c cao, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u00f3c x\u00f9 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Marouane Fellaini s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Fellaini ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 30 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi Man United s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, hay ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c h\u01a1n l\u00e0 v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 1/7 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. Sau th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 do l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn cho m\u00ecnh b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n \u00fd ki\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 nh\u1eadn kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb AC Milan, Arsenal c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Trung Qu\u1ed1c, Fellaini \u0111ang kh\u00e1 &ldquo;\u0111\u1eaft show&rdquo; v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, anh cho bi\u1ebft s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1edbm, ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn khi World Cup 2018 h\u1ea1 m\u00e0n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u00f3c v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i qu\u00e1 b\u1eadn t\u00e2m v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, v\u00ec th\u1ebf t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 1/7, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd bi\u1ebft ngay th\u00f4i&rdquo; &ndash; Marouane Fellaini chia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fellaini s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U\" title=\"Fellaini \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/cuc-bat-ngo-voi-ben-do-tiep-theo-cua-fellaini.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Fellaini s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 theo nh\u1eefng ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u00e1 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn, v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ch\u1edd &ldquo;ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb9p&rdquo; \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 Kristof Terreur &ndash; chuy\u00ean gia \u0111\u01b0a tin v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 &ndash; \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 30 \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford. Anh s\u1ebd gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Man United th\u00eam 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, v\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2020.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 chi ti\u1ebft giao k\u00e8o m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 2 n\u0103m, hay ch\u1ec9 k\u00fd 1 n\u0103m v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng gia h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m. D\u00f9 sao, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, b\u1edfi Fellaini t\u1eebng t\u1ecf th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi ng\u1ea7m \u00e1m ch\u1ec9 Jose Mourinho kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Fellaini s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 m\u1edbi tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Hi\u1ec7n nay, Man United v\u1eabn \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Sergej Milinkovic-Savic, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 h\u01a1n 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/carragher-dt-can-bop-nat-bi-o-tran-dau-toi-469-189525.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/carragher-dt-can-bop-nat-bi-o-tran-dau-toi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/carragher-dt-can-bop-nat-bi-o-tran-dau-toi-469-189525.html\">Carragher: \u0110T Anh c\u1ea7n b\u00f3p n\u00e1t B\u1ec9 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nTheo c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Jamie Carragher, \u0110T Anh n\u00ean b\u1ecf qua nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tong-khu-fellaini-sang-arsenal-fan-mu-mung-nhu-duoc-mua-172-187793.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/30/tong-khu-fellaini-sang-arsenal-fan-mu-mung-nhu-duoc-mua.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tong-khu-fellaini-sang-arsenal-fan-mu-mung-nhu-duoc-mua-172-187793.html\">T\u1ed1ng kh\u1ee9 Fellaini sang Arsenal, fan MU... m\u1eebng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00f9a</span><br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, MU c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1edbt nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Fellaini sang...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3846","checkdouble":"189707"},{"date":"09:29 27/06","title":"Chelsea v\u00e0 Napoli \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u201cchuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng\u201d HLV Sarri","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/28/chelsea-dam-phan-voi-napoli-vi-hlv-sarri.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea v\u00e0 Napoli \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u00ec HLV Sarri. The Blues \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eafn \u0111o r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trong th\u1eddi gian qua v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n thay Conte</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Chelsea. H\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 5 t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a sau. Vi\u1ec7c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00fap FA v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Man United c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 an \u1ee7i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Antonio Conte b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n. \u00d4ng \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p g\u00ec \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn CLB b\u1ecb thi\u1ec7t h\u1ea1i kinh t\u1ebf. Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, Conte c\u00f2n c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u1edbi Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Marina Granovskaia c\u00f9ng 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i 1 c\u1ee7a Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea v\u00e0 Napoli \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u00ec HLV Sarri - ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00ean thay Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea v\u00e0 Napoli \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u00ec HLV Sarri - ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00ean thay Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/19/Chelsea-va-Napoli-dam-phan-vi-HLV-Sarri---nguoi-len-thay-Conte-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Chelsea \u0111ang t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n sa th\u1ea3i Conte</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p thay th\u1ebf Conte \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00ean danh s\u00e1ch trong \u0111\u00f3 s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Laurent Blanc (t\u1ef1 do), Slavisa Jokanovic (Fulham) v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Maurizio Sarri (Napoli). <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Sarri</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e0n, l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Chelsea th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t r\u1eb1ng Sarri l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t ng\u1ed3i gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. V\u00e0 theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Chelsea v\u00e0 Napoli \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u00ec HLV Sarri. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mi\u1ec1n Nam Italia c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng thi\u1ebft tha gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y khi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Carlo Ancelotti l\u00e0m thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Loeno Igsine xac nhan viec HLV Maurizio Sarri den Chelsea.\" title=\"Loeno Igsine x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c HLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/28/chelsea-dam-phan-voi-napoli-vi-hlv-sarri.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Chelsea v\u00e0 Napoli \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u00ec HLV Sarri</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t n\u1eb1m \u1edf vi\u1ec7c Chelsea ph\u1ea3i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Napoli nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1ea1i 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Sarri v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p. H\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc khi m\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho Conte c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ng\u1ed1n s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, Chelsea c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n ch\u1ed1t l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Sarri. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng kh\u00fac m\u1eafc nh\u1ecf v\u00e0 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft. Ngay t\u1eeb gi\u1edd, c\u00f3 tin chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 59 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau nh\u01b0 Gonzalo Higuain, Dries Mertens v\u00e0 Kalidou Koulibaly, \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 cho Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 gh\u1ebf HLV Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-conte-chelsea-chua-the-ky-hop-dong-voi-2-sao-khung-172-188922.html\">V\u00ec Conte Chelsea ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi 2 sao kh\u1ee7ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sergio-ramos-khien-conte-khong-the-dan-dat-real-madrid-180-188726.html\">Sergio Ramos khi\u1ebfn Conte kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real Madrid?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-nham-hlv-argentina-thay-the-conte-172-188459.html\">Chelsea nh\u1eafm HLV Argentina thay th\u1ebf Conte</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-conte-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-real-madrid-172-188046.html\">HLV Conte c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dam-phan-voi-hlv-jokanovic-172-187696.html\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd thay Conte</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3845","checkdouble":"189709"},{"date":"07:16 27/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh: D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2016, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3 xong m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 \u0111\u00e3 vay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh b\u1eb1ng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1eadm 4-0 t\u1ea1i Pleiku. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>1. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng V\u0103n To\u00e0n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn mang t\u00ean Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 V-League, tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 s\u1edbm c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u1edd t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00fang t\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c nh\u01b0 c\u1ed7 xe \u0111ua c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c 1 \u0111\u00e3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n s\u1ef1 \u0111eo b\u00e1m c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u0103ng xu\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u1ea1nh l\u00f9ng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho HAGL.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/1528076018_4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u0103n To\u00e0n l\u00e0 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t trong tr\u1eadn&nbsp;</em><i>HAGL 4-0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</i></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00cdt ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, V\u0103n To\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi bu\u1ed9c D\u01b0\u01a1ng Thanh H\u00e0o ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh, khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf r\u1eddi s\u00e2n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01a1i h\u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi, V\u0103n To\u00e0n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1eefa. Qua \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean BXH V-League 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, V\u0103n To\u00e0n ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a m\u1edf ra chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho HAGL \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 anh, ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc &lsquo;G\u1ed7&rsquo; \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>2. C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi pha s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng ghim th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi CLB Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 s\u01b0u t\u1eadp cho m\u00ecnh 7 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay. T\u00ednh t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u1ed9i ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t V-League, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh c\u1ee7a B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 c\u00f2n k\u00e9m xa th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Oseni (CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i) nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng cao th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cong Phuong HAGL vs Than Quang Ninh\" title=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng HAGL vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/1523280831_5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn HAGL vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i HAGL c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tin vui v\u1edbi HLV Park Hang Seo khi m\u00e0 trong th\u00e2m t\u00e2m \u00f4ng r\u1ea5t tin t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 v\u00e0 \u0111ang k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 v\u00e0 xa h\u01a1n l\u00e0 AFF Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. Ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ea5t \u0111i d\u1ec5, kh\u00f3 v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, CLB HAGL \u0111ang duy tr\u00ec th\u00e0nh t\u00edch 4 th\u1eafng, 2 h\u00f2a v\u00e0 1 b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. \u0110\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi HAGL d\u00f9 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 4-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u0103m nay. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, HAGL v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n l\u00ean cao t\u1eebng h\u1ea1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng M\u1ecf v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-0 t\u1ea1i c\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i s\u1ef1 quen thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n s\u00e2n b\u00e3i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a NHM, m\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed lo\u00e3ng t\u1ea1i Pleiku c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ee5t h\u01a1i khi t\u1edbi ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai thi \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL \u1edf v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y d\u00f9 h\u1ecd m\u1edbi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua HAGL tr\u00ean s\u00e2n C\u1ea9m Ph\u1ea3 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>4. HAGL \u0111ang t\u1ed1t d\u1ea7n l\u00ean v\u1edbi d\u00e0n n\u1ed9i binh<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1 ch\u1ea5p T\u00e2y \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng 100% c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ed9i, tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi t\u1eeb v\u00f9ng \u0110\u00f4ng B\u1eafc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 l\u1edbn, l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin. D\u00f9 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua song m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 l\u00e0 c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng HAGL \u0111ang ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i V-League, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 V\u0103n To\u00e0n hay V\u0103n Thanh v\u1eabn cho th\u1ea5y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, s\u1ef1 kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o trong c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1edbi l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, HAGL c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn xa t\u1ea1i V-League v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 m\u01a1 m\u1ed9ng ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HAGL\" title=\"HAGL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Untitled-8-3819-1530018573.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>D\u00e0n n\u1ed9i binh c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t d\u1ea7n l\u00ean qua t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>5. Cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1ed1p 3 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, HAGL \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean x\u1ebfp \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 6 tr\u00ean BXH v\u1edbi 23 \u0111i\u1ec3m. L\u00fac n\u00e0y kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1p 3 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u1ebfp tr\u00ean HAGL l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Thanh H\u00f3a, Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a v\u00e0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng 25 \u0111i\u1ec3m, c\u00f2n H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf xa nh\u00f3m b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i t\u1edbi 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u00f9 h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea5u. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u0103m nay g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ng\u00e3 ng\u0169 khi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i song cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1eabn di\u1ec5n ra r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng. L\u00fac n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 3 tr\u00ean BXH v\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 chung cu\u1ed9c s\u1ebd ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>Video: HAGL 4-0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh&nbsp;(V\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018)</em></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/26/HAGL-4-0-Quang-Ninh.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/hagl-vs-quang-ninh-vong-16-vleague-2018-372-189604.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/ket-qua-hagl-vs-quang-ninh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/hagl-vs-quang-ninh-vong-16-vleague-2018-372-189604.html\">HAGL 4-0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh (KT): Si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n</span><br>\r\nCLB ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng ngo\u1ea1i binh v\u00e0 to\u00e0n h\u00e0ng c\u00e2y nh\u00e0 l\u00e1 v\u01b0\u1eddn \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng khi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed,...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3844","checkdouble":"189697"},{"date":"07:21 27/06","title":"HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng b\u1ee9c x\u00fac v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-buc-xuc-voi-trong-tai-bat-tran-hagl-40-than-quang-ninh.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng thi\u00ean v\u1ecb ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 HAGL.</h2><h2>HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng b\u1ee9c x\u00fac v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u1edf tr\u1eadn HAGL vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 26/6, CLB HAGL c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1eb7p c\u00e1c v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. Nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin, &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; s\u1edbm c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau pha t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng b\u1ee9c x\u00fac v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Than  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng b\u1ee9c x\u00fac v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Than  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/13/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-khang-dinh-ha-noi-se-vo-dich.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng cho r\u1eb1ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i thi\u00ean v\u1ecb ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 HAGL</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u1edbm, HAGL thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n v\u00e0 h\u1ecd su\u00fdt c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai sau pha b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n. \u1ede t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, s\u1ef1 nhanh nh\u1eb9n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat qu\u00ea H\u1ea3i D\u01b0\u01a1ng bu\u1ed9c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 D\u01b0\u01a1ng Thanh H\u00e0o ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn t\u1edbi t\u1ea5m th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u00fat ra b\u1edfi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Nguy\u1ec5n Ng\u1ecdc Ch\u00e2u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecb d\u1eabn b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi 10 ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb v\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn sau \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i chung cu\u1ed9c 0-4. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o, HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch c\u1ea7m c\u00f2i c\u1ee7a v\u1ecb vua \u00e1o \u0111en \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a Thanh H\u00e0o kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf. \u0110\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tranh ch\u1ea5p b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. C\u00f2n pha b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi\u1ebfn Thanh Hi\u1ec1n ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, theo t\u00f4i th\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a HAGL c\u1ea7n nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1ea5t c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 do th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00ean thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t. HAGL thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn 1 chi\u1ec1u. Kh\u00ed h\u1eadu \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n...&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL, Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb t\u1ee5t xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 4 tr\u00ean BXH, x\u1ebfp sau Thanh H\u00f3a v\u00e0 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng 25 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ecf nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u00ean v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trong nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 3 v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague-c291-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">V-League 2018</span> h\u1ea1 m\u00e0n c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan-168-189697.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan-168-189697.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh: D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2016, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3 xong m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 \u0111\u00e3 vay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh b\u1eb1ng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1eadm 4-0 t\u1ea1i Pleiku. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-hagl-vs-quang-ninh-325-189652.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/clip-ban-thang-hagl-vs-quang-ninh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-hagl-vs-quang-ninh-325-189652.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: HAGL 4-0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh (V\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018)</span><br>\r\nCLB ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng ngo\u1ea1i binh v\u00e0 to\u00e0n h\u00e0ng c\u00e2y nh\u00e0 l\u00e1 v\u01b0\u1eddn \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng khi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed,...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3843","checkdouble":"189698"},{"date":"07:26 27/06","title":"HLV HAGL chia s\u1ebb b\u00ed quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/26/hlv-hagl-chia-se-bi-quyet-giup-hoc-tro-danh-bai-than-quang-ninh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 26/6, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. V\u00e0 HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y?</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 16 V-League di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i 26/6, CLB HAGL c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nhi\u1ec1u duy\u00ean n\u1ee3 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng 0-3, tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eadm 4-0.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV HAGL chia s\u1ebb b\u00ed quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV HAGL chia s\u1ebb b\u00ed quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Untitled-8-3819-1530018573.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV HAGL D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2. &quot;H\u00f4m nay, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed ch\u01a1i d\u1ea1t bi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng cho V\u0103n To\u00e0n. Nh\u00ecn chung, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t&rdquo;, \u00f4ng Ninh t\u00e2m s\u1ef1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft m\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb th\u00eam: &ldquo;Sau m\u1ed7i bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng lu\u00f4n \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t n\u00ean t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2. V\u1edbi 2 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3&nbsp;k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3&nbsp;t\u1ed1t s\u1eafp t\u1edbi&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i th\u00eam v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ngo\u1ea1i binh, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec3n tr\u01b0\u1edfng HAGL kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Osmar d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, c\u00f2n tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Rimario nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, HAGL \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 6 tr\u00ean BXH v\u1edbi 23 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ea7y s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Tam K\u1ef3 g\u1eb7p nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c HAGL th\u01b0\u1eddng thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch, \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan-168-189697.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan-168-189697.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh: D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2016, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3 xong m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 \u0111\u00e3 vay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh b\u1eb1ng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1eadm 4-0 t\u1ea1i Pleiku. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-buc-xuc-voi-trong-tai-bat-tran-hagl-40-than-quang-ninh-168-189698.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-buc-xuc-voi-trong-tai-bat-tran-hagl-40-than-quang-ninh.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-buc-xuc-voi-trong-tai-bat-tran-hagl-40-than-quang-ninh-168-189698.html\">HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng b\u1ee9c x\u00fac v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng thi\u00ean v\u1ecb ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-hagl-vs-quang-ninh-325-189652.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/clip-ban-thang-hagl-vs-quang-ninh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-hagl-vs-quang-ninh-325-189652.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: HAGL 4-0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh (V\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018)</span><br>\r\nCLB ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng ngo\u1ea1i binh v\u00e0 to\u00e0n h\u00e0ng c\u00e2y nh\u00e0 l\u00e1 v\u01b0\u1eddn \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng khi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed,...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3842","checkdouble":"189699"},{"date":"20:56 26/06","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Nainggolan","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/26/chinh-thuc-xac-dinh-ben-do-moi-cua-nainggolan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng tin ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Radja Nainggolan gia nh\u1eadp Inter Milan t\u1eeb CLB AS Roma.\r\n</h2><h2><strong><br>\r\nNainggolan chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Inter<br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Inter Milan, khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Champions League sau 6 n\u0103m v\u1eafng b\u00f3ng. Theo \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a anh ch\u1ec9 r\u1eddi v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 21 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, nh\u01b0ng Inter s\u1ebd c\u00e1c th\u00eam cho Roma 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 Davide Santon v\u00e0 Nicolo Zaniolo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Roma \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00e1n ng\u1ea5y th\u00f3i v\u00f4 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Radja Nainggolan, v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ea9y anh \u0111i ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Serie A \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Premier League, v\u00e0 anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn Inter thay v\u00ec Juventus.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 30 cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi m\u1ed7i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a c\u00e1c C\u0110V Inter c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Radja Nainggolan gia nh\u1eadp Inter Milan v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 b\u00e8o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Radja Nainggolan gia nh\u1eadp Inter Milan v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 b\u00e8o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/WelcomeNinja-Radja-Nainggolan-unveiled-at-Inter-Milan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Radja Nainggolan gia nh\u1eadp Inter Milan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Hy v\u1ecdng ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac c\u00f9ng nhau. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi HLV Spalletti, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y, v\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;L\u00fd do t\u00f4i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn Inter Milan l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cu\u1ed9c g\u1ecdi t\u1eeb Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Ausilio, HLV v\u00e0 Zanetti. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 b\u1ecdn h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y quan tr\u1ecdng, v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn n\u00e0y di\u1ec5n ra r\u1ea5t nhanh ch\u00f3ng, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a cu\u1ed9c phi\u00eau l\u01b0u.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;M\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p g\u1eedi t\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u01b0? T\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 b\u1ecdn h\u1ecd, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. Hy v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c C\u0110V c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo c\u00e1ch t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t \u1edf Serie A v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Champions League. Inter Milan c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1eb1ng sau, v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac ch\u00fang ta tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Radja Nainggolan gia nh\u1eadp Inter Milan, CLB Roma \u0111\u00e3 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Javier Pastore t\u1eeb PSG v\u1ec1 th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/chinh-thuc-emre-can-gia-nhap-juventus-176-189191.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/chinh-thuc-emre-can-gia-nhap-juventus.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/chinh-thuc-emre-can-gia-nhap-juventus-176-189191.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Emre Can gia nh\u1eadp Juventus d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng CNTD</span><br>\r\n\u00cdt ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u00f4ng tin ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Emre Can gia nh\u1eadp Juventus ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp CLB Italia v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/nong-roma-chinh-thuc-hot-tay-tren-muc-tieu-cua-mu-176-188276.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/12/nong-roma-chinh-thuc-hot-tay-tren-muc-tieu-cua-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/nong-roma-chinh-thuc-hot-tay-tren-muc-tieu-cua-mu-176-188276.html\">N\u00d3NG: Roma CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C h\u1edbt tay tr\u00ean m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a M.U</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Rome \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng sao tr\u1ebb Justin Kluivert, con trai c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Patrick Kluivert t\u1eeb Ajax v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 21 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4la.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3841","checkdouble":"189657"},{"date":"18:59 26/06","title":"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 HAGL vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/clip-ban-thang-hagl-vs-quang-ninh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 HAGL vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 16 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2018 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n, clip b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, video highlights t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u HAGL Ho\u00e0ng Anh Gia Lai vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018 18h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 26/6.</h2>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 HAGL vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh: 4-0<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n: V\u0103n To\u00e0n (3', 41'), C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng (43'), Ho\u00e0ng Thanh T\u00f9ng (90'+4)<br>\r\n<hr>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/26/HAGL-phut-44.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\">\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/26/HAGL-4-0-Quang-Ninh.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-3 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin khi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Pleiku. V\u00e0 ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 sau pha tho\u00e1t xu\u1ed1ng r\u1ea5t nhanh c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u1ea3i D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 truy c\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tung ra c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ee7 hi\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n Linh trong t\u1ee9 th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u1edbm gi\u00fap c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL tr\u1edf n\u00ean t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n trong khi Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh l\u1ea1i g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. B\u00e0n g\u1ee1 c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e2u, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ecf su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua th\u1ee9 hai v\u1eabn xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HAGL vs Quang Ninh\" title=\"HAGL vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/ket-qua-hagl-vs-quang-ninh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HAGL c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede pha b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y, V\u0103n To\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1edbi D\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0103n H\u00e0o bu\u1ed9c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb tru\u1ea5t quy\u1ec1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t sau \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf ch\u01a1i h\u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi, kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u00eam hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1eefa do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n \u1edf ph\u00fat 41 v\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf ph\u00fat 43.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf ghi 3 b\u00e0n trong hi\u1ec7p 1 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i h\u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7p 2 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i. Do \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eadm n\u00ean HAGL ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i ch\u1eadm l\u1ea1i sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1ea3i lao.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng d\u00e1m n\u1eafm b\u1eaft l\u1ea5y th\u1eddi c\u01a1 d\u00e2ng cao b\u1edfi \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 10 ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. N\u1ebfu qu\u00e1 m\u1ea3i m\u00ea t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng th\u00ec nguy c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ecf b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi th\u00eam l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t, CLB HAGL v\u1eabn l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 khung th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n Linh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edbi ph\u00fat 57, V\u0103n To\u00e0n ch\u00fat n\u1eefa l\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hattrick n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng ra tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1ea1ch v\u1ed9i v\u00e0 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tung ra c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 b\u1ed3i t\u1ed1t.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>\u00cdt ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea3 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy nhi\u00ean c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 ch\u1eadm. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL mi\u1ec7t m\u00e0i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh c\u0169ng su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng danh d\u1ef1 tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Nghi\u00eam Xu\u00e2n T\u00fa l\u1ea1i \u0111i tr\u00fang x\u00e0 ngang khung th\u00e0nh V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0 th\u00ec \u0111\u00fang \u1edf ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0o thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ho\u00e0ng Thanh T\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c c\u1ef1c nhanh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00e9o g\u00f3c l\u00e0m rung l\u01b0\u1edbi khung th\u00e0nh Tu\u1ea5n Linh th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c 4-0, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3 xong m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 thua 0-3 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 6 tr\u00ean BXH v\u1edbi 23 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 16 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3840","checkdouble":"189647"},{"date":"19:16 26/06","title":"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i khi b\u1ecb x\u1ebfp v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng th\u1ea5p t\u1ea1i ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/26/dt-olympic-viet-nam-gap-bat-loi-khi-bi-xep-vao-nhom-hat-giong-thap-tai-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, H\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3ng Olympic ch\u00e2u \u00c1 (OCA) \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u1eddi gian b\u1ed1c th\u0103m chia b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018. V\u00e0 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng t\u1eed th\u1ea7n khi b\u1ecb x\u1ebfp \u1edf nh\u00f3m 3.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i khi n\u1eb1m \u1edf nh\u00f3m 3</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n, HLV Park Hang Seo v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 - s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i v\u1ed1n d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung 3 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i khi b\u1ecb x\u1ebfp v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng th\u1ea5 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i khi b\u1ecb x\u1ebfp v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng th\u1ea5 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/u23-vietnam_ep0r479u5w6d1n97ckg00hkcj.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1ecb x\u1ebfp v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng th\u1ee9 3 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e0y \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1ecb x\u1ebfp v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng th\u1ee9 3 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y sau bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a H\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3ng Olympic ch\u00e2u \u00c1 (OCA).\u00a0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p>V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. <o:p></o:p>\u1ede nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng th\u1ee9 3, ngo\u00e0i Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n c\u00f3 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Malaysia, L\u00e0o v\u00e0 Philippines. 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng n\u1eb1m \u1edf nh\u00f3m n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Jordan, Yemen, Bangladesh v\u00e0 H\u1ed3ng K\u00f4ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00f3m 1 s\u1ebd g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u01b0u t\u00fa nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c g\u1ed3m nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Syria, Uzbekistan, \u1ea2 R\u1eadp X\u00ea \u00dat, Iran, Iraq c\u00f9ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">8 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf nh\u00f3m 2 bao g\u1ed3m Olympic Trung Qu\u1ed1c, Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean, Oman, Qatar, Bahrain, UAE, Kyrgyzstan v\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y g\u1ed3m Nepal, \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9, Campuchia, \u0110\u00f4ng Timor, Tajikistan, Singapore, Myanmar v\u00e0 Palestine. \u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">32 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd chia th\u00e0nh 8 b\u1ea3ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi th\u1ec3 th\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 VCK World Cup \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn ra 16 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out. L\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m chia b\u1ea3ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 15/07, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 14/08/2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tu-choi-sang-nga-xem-world-cup-vi-dai-cuc-168-189362.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/hlv-park-hang-seo-tu-choi-sang-nga-xem-world-cup-vi-dai-cuc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tu-choi-sang-nga-xem-world-cup-vi-dai-cuc-168-189362.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i sang Nga xem World Cup v\u00ec \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee5c</span><br>\r\nTheo chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y t\u1eeb T\u1ed5ng th\u01b0 k\u00fd VFF L\u00ea Ho\u00e0i Anh th\u00ec HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng sang Nga xem World Cup theo l\u1eddi m\u1eddi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 m\u00e0 \u00f4ng s\u1ebd d\u00e0nh th\u1eddi gian chu\u1ea9n...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-chi-dich-danh-3-cau-thu-co-the-lo-hen-voi-asiad-2018-168-187949.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/20/hlv-park-hang-seo-chi-dich-danh-3-cau-thu-co-the-lo-hen-voi-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-chi-dich-danh-3-cau-thu-co-the-lo-hen-voi-asiad-2018-168-187949.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00edch danh 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, HLV Park Hang Seo cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00ean h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Th\u1ea7y Park s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5m V\u0103n L\u00e2m hay B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng cho ASIAD 2018?</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Nh\u01b0ng li\u1ec7u HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn ai b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh cho \u0110T Olympic...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguyen-tien-linh-manh-ghep-con-thieu-cua-thay-park-168-187368.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/nguyen-tien-linh-manh-ghep-con-thieu-cua-thay-park.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguyen-tien-linh-manh-ghep-con-thieu-cua-thay-park-168-187368.html\">Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh: M\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park?</span><br>\r\n\u0110i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t c\u00fa poker b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i V-League, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi khen t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3839","checkdouble":"189648"},{"date":"20:01 26/06","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 26/6: MU nh\u1eadn c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1ee5 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2016/12/21/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-266-mu-nhan-cau-tra-loi-vu-hau-ve-35-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 26/6.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU nh\u1eadn c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1ee5 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 266 MU nh\u1eadn c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1ee5 Jose Gaya h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 266 MU nh\u1eadn c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1ee5 Jose Gaya h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/15/Diem-tin-bong-da-toi-266-MU-nhan-cau-tra-loi-vu-Jose-Gaya-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Valencia tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Jose Gaya cho M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTheo Don Balon, Valencia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i Jose Gaya cho M.U. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Milinkovic-Savic</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mundo Deportivo, Barca \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch h\u1ecfi mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mundo Deportivo c\u1ee7a Lazio, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-bat-ngo-muon-chi-80-trieu-euro-mua-pogba-serbia-180-189646.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/9/barca-bat-ngo-muon-chi-80-trieu-euro-mua-pogba-serbia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-bat-ngo-muon-chi-80-trieu-euro-mua-pogba-serbia-180-189646.html\">Barca b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Pogba Serbia</span><br>\r\nBarca mu\u1ed1n mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MU mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Pogba l\u1ea5y Verratti</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo The Sun, \u0111\u1ec3 nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7&nbsp; Marco Verratti, M.U ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn hy sinh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf mu\u1ed1n trao \u0111\u1ed5i ngang gi\u1eefa c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua l\u1ea1i Thiago Alcantara</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thiago Alcantara dinh chan thuong nghiem trong\" title=\"Thiago Alcantara d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/23/real-madrid-nham-nguoi-cu-barca-nang-cap-tuyen-giua.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua l\u1ea1i Thiago Alcantara</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Don Balon, Barca mu\u1ed1n mua l\u1ea1i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Thiago Alcantara, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Bayern Munich. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Inter k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Nainggolan t\u1eeb Roma</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Inter Milan \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Radja Nainggolan t\u1eeb Roma, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Sarri s\u1eafp k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mirror, Chelsea s\u1ebd b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Maurizio Sarri trong 48 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi, ngay sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mang t\u00ean Daniele Rugani t\u1eeb Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Alex Sandro</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Sport Mediaset, Juventus s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Alex Sandro v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52.8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, hi\u1ec7n M.U v\u00e0 Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal kh\u00f4ng mua Lewis Dunk</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal muon mua Lewis Dunk\" title=\"Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Lewis Dunk\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/arsenal-nham-sao-brighton-nang-cap-hang-thu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i mua Lewis Dunk</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mirror, Arsenal s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Lewis Dunk c\u1ee7a Brighton. HLV Unai Emery kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c thay v\u00ec chi 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Brighton.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-nham-sao-brighton-nang-cap-hang-thu-172-189633.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/arsenal-nham-sao-brighton-nang-cap-hang-thu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-nham-sao-brighton-nang-cap-hang-thu-172-189633.html\">Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Arsenal nh\u1eafm sao Brighton n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</span><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Lewis Dunk th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao. Theo Mirror, HLV Unai Emery kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Loftus-Cheek&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Telegraph kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ruben Loftus-Cheek, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Crystal Palace theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3838","checkdouble":"189651"},{"date":"18:26 26/06","title":"Barca b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro mua \"Pogba Serbia\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/9/barca-bat-ngo-muon-chi-80-trieu-euro-mua-pogba-serbia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Iniesta</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Iniesta \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay Barca sau nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3, s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/21/Barca-muon-mua-Sergej-Milinkovic-Savic-voi-gia-80-trieu-euro-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Iniesta\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Ernesto Valverde \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Iniesta. Don Balon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi Christian Eriksen c\u1ee7a Tottenham ho\u1eb7c Miralem Pjanic c\u1ee7a Juventus, song nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111em l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u kh\u1ea3 quan.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTottenham v\u00e0 Juventus \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Eriksen v\u00e0 Pjanic c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i. Song song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, Barca \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca quan t\u00e2m Sergej Milinkovic-Savic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mundo Deportivo, Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. HLV Valverde \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n Barca \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 Camp Nou.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Milinkovic-Savic\" title=\"Milinkovic-Savic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/9/barca-bat-ngo-muon-chi-80-trieu-euro-mua-pogba-serbia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca quan t\u00e2m Milinkovic-Savic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Lazio, anh ghi t\u1edbi 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Serie A. Milinkovic-Savic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng, chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i, ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Iniesta \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-hang-hot-serie-a-172-174713.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m Milinkovic-Savic</span>, song nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin cho r\u1eb1ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat lui trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Lazio y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi ra 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia, song s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecb Lazio t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia nhanh ch\u00f3ng kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLazio \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ee7 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 Milinkovic-Savic Barca s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3837","checkdouble":"189646"},{"date":"23:49 26/06","title":"Kaka x\u00fai Neymar b\u1ecf PSG gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/24/kaka-xui-neymar-bo-psg-gia-nhap-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Brazil l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khuy\u00ean \u0111\u00e0n em \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00ean s\u1edbm gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u anh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 mong mu\u1ed1n.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Neymar s\u1edbm b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi ch\u1ec9 sau v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n m\u1ed9t n\u0103m ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi 222 tri\u1ec7u Euro sang Paris Saint-Germain. \u0110\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p kh\u00f4ng cao c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p hay nh\u1eefng v\u1ee5 l\u00f9m x\u00f9m nh\u01b0 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, ng\u00f4i sao Brazil ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i ngay \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Neymar c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Barcelona nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Real Madrid m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng m\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u01a1n b\u00e3o t\u1ed1 th\u1ecbnh n\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb c\u00e1c Cules. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kaka khuy\u00ean Neymar gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid chia tay PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kaka khuy\u00ean Neymar gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid chia tay PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/kaka-xui-neymar-bo-psg-gia-nhap-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kaka khuy\u00ean Neymar gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, ch\u00ednh CLB ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 t\u1eeb thu\u1edf nh\u1ecf c\u1ee7a Neymar v\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e2ng cao v\u1ecb th\u1ebf v\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh, danh ti\u1ebfng thay th\u1ebf ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng Cristiano Ronaldo hay Gareth Bale, ng\u00f4i sao Brazil kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m ng\u01a1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady m\u00e0 Kaka khuy\u00ean Neymar gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid theo ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t. C\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 h\u00e0o hoa \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n em \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1edbm c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 c\u1ee7a anh, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 n\u00f3 \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn cho anh nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m bu\u1ed3n h\u01a1n vui.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kaka cho bi\u1ebft: \u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Neymar v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u00ean can \u0111\u1ea3m quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh theo nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n. N\u1ebfu ra \u0111i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta s\u1ebd n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng Neymar gia nh\u1eadp PSG ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e2y c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid.\u201d <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn v\u00ec nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y theo t\u00f4i l\u00e0 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 26 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00edn \u1edf c\u1ea3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 t\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean th\u1ee9 Neymar c\u1ea7n l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh cao, nh\u01b0 Real Madrid.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barca-muon-so-huu-dong-doi-cua-neymar-sau-world-cup-2018-172-189666.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/28/barca-muon-so-huu-dong-doi-cua-neymar-sau-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barca-muon-so-huu-dong-doi-cua-neymar-sau-world-cup-2018-172-189666.html\">Barca mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Neymar sau World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nTheo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, CLB Barca \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gabriel Jesus c\u1ee7a Man City trong  k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3836","checkdouble":"189667"}]}